name: Flutter Design Patterns
shortDescription: An open-source Flutter application that showcases all 23 designs patterns in Object-Oriented Programming described in the Gang of Four book "Design Patterns: Elements of Reusable Object-Oriented Software".
longDescription: An open-source Flutter application that showcases all 23 designs patterns in Object-Oriented Programming described in the Gang of Four book "Design Patterns: Elements of Reusable Object-Oriented Software".
